ence, P. (2012) </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">The Legal Problems and Mental Hea</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">lth Needs of Youth Advice Service Users</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">. Youth Access.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 17pt; text-indent:-17pt"><a name="_ftn13"></a><a href="#_ftnref13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">Pleasence, P. (2011) </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Civil legal problems: Young People, Social Exclusion and Crime</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">. Youth Access and Law Centres Federation.</span></p><h2 style="background-color:#ffffff; margin:0pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid"><a name="_ftn14"></a><a href="#_ftnref14">[14]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">No Recourse to Public Funds Network (Sept. 2013)</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal">Shadow Impact </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal">Assessments for the Proposed Residence Test</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal">.</span></h2></body></html>